quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  10,26,"Hino woodani Й“en moЖҙЖҙimЙ“e (golle) moЖҙЖҙere e Й“eydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Aljanna Й“en, kamЙ“e ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e ton"
  10,27,"ЖҒen faggitiiЙ“e boneeji Й—in, njoЙ“di bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay Й“e, Alanaa Й“e immorde ka Alla hay daЙ—ndoowo, A sikkay geece maЙ“Й“e Й—en ko hippiraa ko taЖҙontinnde jemma niЙ“Й“utuЙ—o. Ko Й“en woni yimЙ“e Yiite, kamЙ“e ko luttooЙ“e ton"
  10,28,"Г‘alnde Men mooЙ“indirta Й“e denndaangal, refti Men wi'ana Й“en sirkunooЙ“e : \"Wonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidiiЙ“e mon.\" Men senndindira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, kafidiiЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en wi'a : \"Wonaa menen wonunoЙ—on e rewude"
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, men laatinoke welsindiiЙ“e gaay e dewe mon Й—en"
  10,30,Ko Й—on wonkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. ЖҒe ruttitee ka Alla GiЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on ka goonga; ko Й“e wonunoo fefindaande kon majjira Й“e
  10,31,"Maaku : \"Ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Kaa ko hommbo jeyti nanЙ—e Й—en e giiЙ—e Й—en, ko hommbo kadi yaltinta ko wuuri e nder ko maayi, o yaltina ka maayi e nder ko wuuri, ko hommbo kadi yiilata fiyaaku on?\" ЖҒe wi'ay : \"Ko Alla\". Maaku : \"E on hulatah"
  10,32,"Ko on Й—on mo'on Alla, woni jeyЙ—o on e goonga. Ko honЙ—um woni Й“aawo goonga si wanaa majjere? Ko honno firlitirte Й—on"
  10,33,"Ko wano nii konngol Joomi maa ngol jojjiri e hoore faasiqinЙ“e Й“en :wonnde pellet, Й“e gomЙ—intah"
  10,34,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en on mo no fuЙ—Й—a tagu refi o ruttita ngu [Й“aawo maayde]?\" Maaku :\"Ko Alla fuЙ—Й—ata tagu ngun refti O ruttita ngu. Ko honno fefindara Й—on [faade e meere]"
  10,35,"Maaku : \"Hara no e kafidiiЙ“e mon Й“en on fewnoowo e goonga?\" Maaku: \"Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on fewnoowo e goonga Й“uri handude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewantaa (hoore mon) si wanaa on fewna? Ko heЙ“i on sifa no Гұaawirton"
  10,36,Ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke Й—en duncataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko Й“e gollata
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaare fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde goonginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  10,38,"Kaa Й“e wi'ay : \"O fefindi nde?\" Maaku : \"Addee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo haЙ—tanЙ—on gaanin Alla, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  10,39,"Ko woni, Й“e fennii ko Й“e huЙ“indaaki ganndal mun, [ko Й“e fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araali Й“e taho. Ko wano non adinooЙ“e Й“en fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane tooГұooЙ“e Й“en wa'unoo"
  10,40,"No e maЙ“Й“e gomЙ—inЙ—o nde, no e maЙ“Й“e kadi mo gomЙ—inaa nde. Ko Joomi maa Й“uri anndude bonnooЙ“e Й“en"
  10,41,"Si Й“e fennii ma, maaku : \"No woodani lam (njoЙ“di) golle am, no woodani on (njoЙ“di) kuuЙ—e mon. Onon ko on daЙ—ndiiЙ“e ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi daЙ—ndiiЙ—o(kisdo) ko golloton"
  10,42,"No e maЙ“Й“e Й“en heЙ—otooЙ“e ma. E ko annannta faaЙ—u Й“e Й“en, hay tawii Й“e haqqiltah"
  10,43,"No e maЙ“Й“e on ndaaroowo ma. E ko an fewnata bunЙ—o on, hay si wonii Й“e yi'atah"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla tooГұirtah yimЙ“e Й“en huunde, ko woni, ko yimЙ“e Й“en tooГұata ko ko'e mun"
  10,45,"Г‘alnde O mooЙ“oyta Й“e, wa'ata kona si Й“e ГұiiЙ“aano si wanaa sa'a gooto e Гұalorma, hiЙ“e anndandira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. GomЙ—ii Й“en fennuЙ“e kawral Alla ngal sooyii, Й“e wonaano feewuЙ“e"
  10,46,"Si Men hollii ma yoga e kon ko Men fodi Й“e, maa Й—um Men Жҙettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka Amen woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e. Refti Alla ko seediiЙ—o e kon ko Й“e gollata"
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala NulaaЙ—o. Si NulaaЙ—o maЙ“Й“e on arii, Гұaawiree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al, kamЙ“e Й“e tooГұetaake"
  10,48,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee Fodoore, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  10,49,"Maaku : \"Mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal maЙ“Й“e ngal arii, Й“e nennirantaake saa'a Й“e ardinantaake kadi"
  10,50,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si lepte Makko Й—en ardii on jemma maa Гұalorma, ko honЙ—um bomЙ“e Й“en hawjiranta Й—e"
  10,51,"E ko tuma Й—e yani gomЙ—in ton Й—e? E ko jooni non, gomЙ—ii on laatinoke hawjirЙ“e Й—um"
  10,52,"Refti tooГұuЙ“e Й“en wi'anee : \"MeeЙ—ee lepte luttugol. Hara on yoЙ“ete si wanaa kon wonunoЙ—on e faggitaade"